snippet.title: Songbringer Alpha Gameplay Trailer v4
snippet.description:
This is the official alpha-version gameplay trailer for Songbringer, a procedurally-generated Zelda-inspired pixel action adventure RPG coming 2016 to Steam for PC, Mac and Linux. 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/367080
http://songbringer.com
